Package Player

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddJList
    this class create a scrollable JList with all the tracks and all the informations about the tracks
    Buttons
    this class implements the actionlistener and the runnable interfaces and create 7 buttons (play , stop, pause, next track , previus track , volume up , volume down)
    Collection
    this class implements a collection(with collection name ,the playback and a list of tracks)
    mainclass  
    Menu
    this class implements actionlistener and create the menu bar for the player
    Track
    this class implements a track(with title , path , notes and duration)
